                <h1 align=left>Citing SHARPpy</h1>
                <p align=left>
Many contributors have put an immeasurable amount of time into developing this software package. If SHARPpy is used to develop a weather product or contributes to research that leads to a scientific publication, please acknowledge the SHARPpy project by citing the code. You can use this ready-made citation entry or provide a link back to this website.
</p>
